1
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:32,720
(Episode 39)

2
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:44,200
Sister Hua,

3
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:46,520
get in the car with my mom first.

4
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:48,560
I have a few words with Yan.

5
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:49,440
Sure.

6
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:51,440
Yan, we are leaving now.

7
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:53,200
-Let's go.
-We'll get going then

8
00:01:54,960 --> 00:01:56,240
Come on, Sister Hua. Be careful.

9
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:57,600
It's okay. I can walk myself.

10
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:58,840
It's tiring for you to do it yourself.

11
00:01:58,920 --> 00:01:59,840
I'm fine.

12
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:05,240
Yan, we are leaving now.

13
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:07,920
Follow Dr. Xiao's instructions

14
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:09,800
at the nursing home.

15
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:11,160
Don't make decisions by yourself.

16
00:02:12,440 --> 00:02:13,800
Are you really okay

17
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,200
on your own?

18
00:02:16,160 --> 00:02:17,000
Don't worry.

19
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:19,360
It's more convenient for me to be alone.

20
00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:20,520
Don't forget,

21
00:02:20,600 --> 00:02:21,680
Guang is here with me.

22
00:02:24,160 --> 00:02:25,320
Call me at once

23
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:26,800
if anything comes up.

24
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:28,400
I will come back to help you immediately.

25
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:30,840
Relax. Don't worry about me.

26
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:32,520
What matters most

27
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:34,080
is to take good care of your mom

28
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:35,160
at the nursing home.

29
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:36,400
As a matter of fact,

30
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:38,040
take care of Jiang Ze as well.

31
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,200
Yan.

32
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:43,680
How is it going?

33
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:45,360
I have contacted Dr. Xiao and Jiang Ze.

34
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:46,880
We will join them at the hospital later,

35
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:48,160
then we will go to the nursing home
together.

36
00:02:49,200 --> 00:02:50,000
Go on then.

37
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:51,320
Okay.

38
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:08,800
Alright, we should go now.

39
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,040
Let's go.

40
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,040
Alright.

41
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:52,720
The procedures are done.

42
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:54,760
Dr. Xiao,

43
00:03:55,160 --> 00:03:56,280
thank you so much.

44
00:03:56,760 --> 00:03:57,880
I wouldn't know

45
00:03:58,200 --> 00:03:59,040
what to do

46
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,320
without your help today.

47
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:02,000
You haven't done the procedures before.

48
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,240
Of course you wouldn't know the process.

49
00:04:03,760 --> 00:04:05,280
I have worked in the hospital
for many years,

50
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:07,600
so this is a piece of cake for me.

51
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:13,080
Xiaomeng, I really want to help you

52
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:14,600
but...

53
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:16,800
I can't.

54
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:19,240
You should take a rest.

55
00:04:20,880 --> 00:04:21,840
Alright.

56
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,880
We should get to the room now.

57
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:25,360
Don't just stand here.

58
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:27,040
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

59
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:52,920
I have cured many of

60
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,680
these kinds of patients.

61
00:04:55,760 --> 00:04:57,640
After two rounds of treatment,

62
00:04:57,880 --> 00:04:59,040
she will get better.

63
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:02,000
and she might recover her memory.

64
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:06,200
That's great. Thank you, Professor David.

65
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:07,720
This way.

66
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:08,880
What did they say?

67
00:05:08,960 --> 00:05:10,200
I didn't understand anything.

68
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:12,880
Sister Hua, they said that

69
00:05:13,080 --> 00:05:14,720
mom would get well soon.

70
00:05:15,760 --> 00:05:16,720
That's great.

71
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:17,600
Right.

72
00:05:18,640 --> 00:05:20,840
The foreign doctor is really good!

73
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:23,400
-Mom.
-It's good that you'll recover.

74
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,640
-Don't worry.
-I'll get you some food.

75
00:05:33,320 --> 00:05:34,120
How is that?

76
00:05:35,320 --> 00:05:36,200
It still hurts a little

77
00:05:36,400 --> 00:05:37,760
but it's better than before.

78
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:40,560
You are recovering well,

79
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:42,560
yet your leg is still weak.

80
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:44,560
I'll arrange physiotherapy for you.

81
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:46,320
Is your family going to be
with you for the therapy?

82
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:51,000
Doctor, I will be with him.

83
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:54,240
Good. In your case, you just need to

84
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:55,400
do physiotherapy regularly,

85
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:57,440
and your leg will recover
completely before long.

86
00:05:58,200 --> 00:05:59,480
That's great, Jiang Ze.

87
00:05:59,880 --> 00:06:00,800
I know that

88
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:02,600
you'll get well soon.

89
00:06:03,320 --> 00:06:05,200
I told you I'm not that fragile.

90
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:09,000
Alright. That's it for now.

91
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:10,440
Call me

92
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:11,400
if anything happens.

93
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:13,360
-Sure.
-Thank you, doctor.

94
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:19,000
Do you want some fruit?

95
00:06:19,320 --> 00:06:20,400
Sure, thank you.

96
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:28,440
It has been a long time

97
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:29,600
since our workers stopped working

98
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:31,080
due to shortage of funding.

99
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:32,800
It has a great impact

100
00:06:32,880 --> 00:06:34,120
on the reputation of Shenghai group.

101
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,600
Our public relations department

102
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:36,600
has gotten in touch

103
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:37,520
with the workers' representative

104
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:39,840
and tried to negotiate with them.

105
00:06:40,280 --> 00:06:42,840
But it's not very effective.

106
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:44,360
Chairman Zhou,

107
00:06:45,280 --> 00:06:46,280
our lack of funding has caused

108
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:48,320
a breach of acquisition contracts.

109
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:50,640
Our vendors are pushing us every day.

110
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,200
If this goes on,

111
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:53,920
I think they may

112
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:55,600
take legal actions against us.

113
00:07:01,080 --> 00:07:02,280
This is the toughest time

114
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:03,600
for Shenghai Group.

115
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:05,760
But I think we may see
the light at the end of the tunnel soon.

116
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:07,280
I am seeking

117
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,600
partnership with other companies.

118
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:09,880
Once the funding is in place,

119
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,560
the issues we're facing

120
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:12,840
will be resolved immediately.

121
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:15,720
We have to calm the workers down.

122
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:17,440
Try to raise some funds first

123
00:07:17,520 --> 00:07:18,600
and pay the workers some money first.

124
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,080
Regarding the vendors.

125
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:21,280
Talk to them.

126
00:07:21,520 --> 00:07:22,800
After all, we've partnered with them for
such a long time.

127
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:24,040
I think it should not be a big problem

128
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,280
for them to hang with us for another
while.

129
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:26,360
Thank you very much.

130
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,280
Chairman Zhou,

131
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:31,840
Vice president Jiang has just sent
a message in the group

132
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:33,880
to notify us of
an urgent board meeting tomorrow.

133
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:37,240
(Notification of an Urgent Board Meeting)

134
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,560
(Shenghai Group Holdings Ltd.)

135
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:42,280
(Jiang Qiancheng, September 6th, 2017)

136
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:45,160
Chairman Zhou, what should we do?

137
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:06,040
Even if you tortured yourself

138
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:07,200
the problems won't be solved.

139
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:20,360
The best case scenario would be

140
00:08:21,640 --> 00:08:23,280
a failure in the PR strategy

141
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:25,840
which will intensify the impact of
the strike,

142
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:28,120
causing Shenghai's share price to plunge.

143
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:31,640
Jiang Qingcheng would then conspire

144
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:33,000
with the board members to dismiss me
as CEO.

145
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:35,320
If this is the best scenario,

146
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:36,720
what about the worst case scenario?

147
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,000
Jiang Qingcheng

148
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,120
would acquire a massive external capital

149
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,680
to boost his shares in Shenghai.

150
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:47,000
My equity and Xiaomeng's

151
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:47,960
would be diluted.

152
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:50,560
When Jiang Qingcheng's owns

153
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:51,640
more shares in Shenghai than me,

154
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:54,680
he will take over Shenghai Group.

155
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:57,400
You won't let him succeed.

156
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:05,800
Jiang Qingcheng will try every way

157
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:07,200
to dismiss me as CEO.

158
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:09,280
I am in a very difficult position now.

159
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:11,440
But no matter what,

160
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,760
I will guard Shenghai Group

161
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,880
and protect Xiaomeng's equity.

162
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:21,120
Why are you sighing?

163
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:23,640
Don't you not trust me?

164
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:24,800
Brother Yan,

165
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,400
if I don't trust you,

166
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:27,560
you wouldn't be able to see me

167
00:09:27,680 --> 00:09:28,800
in such a critical moment.

168
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:44,760
Thank you very much, Professor David.

169
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,800
I really appreciate your help

170
00:09:46,880 --> 00:09:48,840
for communicating with the patient.

171
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:51,280
Later, I will have
a case discussion meeting

172
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,520
in the room over there.

173
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:53,800
I hope you can join.

174
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:57,040
Then we can have a talk about
Chinese traditional medicine

175
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:58,200
and western medicine.

176
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,000
It's my pleasure.

177
00:10:00,160 --> 00:10:01,600
See you later at the meeting room.

178
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:03,200
Okay. So, don't miss it.

179
00:10:03,920 --> 00:10:04,720
Be sure to come.

180
00:10:05,040 --> 00:10:06,320
Yeah, here's the report.

181
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,400
See you. Bye.

182
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:08,440
-See you.
-Bye.

183
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:11,120
Xiaomeng.

184
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,840
Sister Hua, keep an eye on my mom.

185
00:10:15,920 --> 00:10:16,800
I'll be back soon.

186
00:10:22,760 --> 00:10:23,600
Dr. Xiao.

187
00:10:23,920 --> 00:10:25,160
What did the foreign expert

188
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:26,160
say to you?

189
00:10:27,040 --> 00:10:28,960
There's some difference between
Chinese and western treatment.

190
00:10:29,160 --> 00:10:31,320
There are also different approaches
for particular cases.

191
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,920
I will list all the things to watch
out for later.

192
00:10:33,040 --> 00:10:34,360
Then I will post it in the patient's room.

193
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:35,640
You should also tell Sister Hua

194
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:36,800
to pay attention

195
00:10:36,880 --> 00:10:37,720
when she looks after Aunt Ye.

196
00:10:38,920 --> 00:10:39,960
I'm glad you are here,

197
00:10:40,160 --> 00:10:41,040
so that my mom's treatment

198
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:42,040
has gone very well.

199
00:10:42,560 --> 00:10:43,560
Don't say that.

200
00:10:43,920 --> 00:10:45,120
Aunt Ye has helped me since my childhood.

201
00:10:45,560 --> 00:10:46,800
I'm just returning the favor.

202
00:10:47,920 --> 00:10:49,160
Professor David said that

203
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,680
Aunt Ye will recover very soon.

204
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:52,280
All we need now is

205
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:53,760
time and patience.

206
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:56,240
You have to believe that

207
00:10:56,760 --> 00:10:58,360
Aunt Ye will recover very soon.

208
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:00,280
I do believe that

209
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:01,640
mom will get well soon.

210
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:04,840
We will treat Aunt Ye

211
00:11:04,920 --> 00:11:06,200
in the following three approaches.

212
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:08,520
Firstly, medicine

213
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:10,160
with a dietary therapy.

214
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:11,800
Secondly, counseling.

215
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,160
Alright.

216
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:29,160
I'm late. Let's begin.

217
00:11:36,640 --> 00:11:38,280
Since Chairman Zhou is here,

218
00:11:38,520 --> 00:11:40,720
let's start the board meeting.

219
00:11:41,520 --> 00:11:42,520
Everyone,

220
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:45,640
the investment in the sports arena project

221
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:48,240
has caused great tension

222
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:49,640
to our funding.

223
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:52,160
Also, the workers' strike

224
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,480
has been violently suppressed

225
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:55,600
by Chairman Zhou

226
00:11:56,400 --> 00:11:57,600
and it has a great impact.

227
00:11:57,960 --> 00:12:00,120
The share price of our company

228
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:02,560
has dropped to
the lowest point in the last three years.

229
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:03,960
The total value of our assets

230
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:06,120
has shrunk by 20%.

231
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:07,760
If the situation goes on,

232
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:09,560
our company won't survive.

233
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:13,400
Yes, it has never been
as tough as this year.

234
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:16,000
Yes. Our efforts in the last year is
in vain.

235
00:12:16,920 --> 00:12:17,800
Stop talking.

236
00:12:18,680 --> 00:12:19,960
Listen to Vice president Jiang.

237
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:24,360
We can no longer withstand the pressure

238
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:26,200
from the board members and the public,

239
00:12:26,520 --> 00:12:27,760
so I've called for this

240
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:29,920
urgent board meeting

241
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:31,080
to discuss the issue of

242
00:12:31,160 --> 00:12:32,360
the lack of funding.

243
00:12:32,920 --> 00:12:34,560
With my efforts,

244
00:12:34,880 --> 00:12:37,400
currently Fanhai Capital,

245
00:12:37,640 --> 00:12:40,680
Shenjian Investment, and Luye Industrial

246
00:12:41,040 --> 00:12:43,400
