250
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:52,600
of shares by these companies.

251
00:12:53,280 --> 00:12:54,160
I agree.

252
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:56,080
This is great news.

253
00:12:56,640 --> 00:12:58,520
Fanhai Capital, Shenjian Investment

254
00:12:58,600 --> 00:12:59,840
and Luye Industrial

255
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:02,240
are the biggest investment companies

256
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:03,520
in our city.

257
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:05,560
Under such unfavorable circumstances,

258
00:13:05,760 --> 00:13:07,400
a massive investment of

259
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:09,800
six billion

