is definitely a great relief to us.

261
00:13:14,640 --> 00:13:15,440
Vice president Jiang,

262
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:17,520
you are the savior of Shenghai.

263
00:13:17,760 --> 00:13:18,920
Us small board members

264
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:20,200
can't be happier.

265
00:13:20,400 --> 00:13:21,920
We can't be happier.

266
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:24,360
Yes, such good news.

267
00:13:24,880 --> 00:13:25,840
That's right.

268
00:13:29,320 --> 00:13:31,560
Dear board members, hear me out.

269
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:33,640
Perhaps Chairman Zhou

270
