271
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:36,840
In order to get Shenghai

272
00:13:36,920 --> 00:13:38,320
out of the current plight,

273
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:39,920
I must say,

274
00:13:40,440 --> 00:13:42,760
funding is the most common challenge

275
00:13:42,840 --> 00:13:43,920
for real estate companies.

276
00:13:44,280 --> 00:13:46,360
Yet there is no other company

277
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:49,400
who would make such a mess

278
00:13:49,560 --> 00:13:51,240
with the PR incident.

279
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:52,800
I have to say that

280
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:55,920
now I seriously doubt

281
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:59,520
the capability of Chairman Zhou.

282
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:01,360
I propose

283
00:14:01,880 --> 00:14:03,800
for the development of Shenghai Group,

284
00:14:04,040 --> 00:14:05,440
we should discuss

